   <tp:treatment-sec sec-type="discussion">
      <p>
Remarks
</p>
      <p>
We were unable to examine any 
type
specimens of 
<tp:taxon-name>
Miridiba newari
</tp:taxon-name>
. However, the original description and illustration of male genitalia given by 
Sabatinelli &amp; Migliaccio (1982)
prove that this species belongs to Morphotype I “ 
<tp:taxon-name>
Trichophora
</tp:taxon-name>
”.
</p>
